OL,3,CBoy aged 9 among three children
OL,4,Cdetained following disorder
OL,6,FMasked youths have thrown stones at
OL,7,Fvehicles, damaged a bus stop with
OL,8,Fpetrol bombs, and blocked a road with
OL,9,Fburning pallets in Londonderry.
OL,11,FThe police said they received reports
OL,12,Fof disturbances on the Glengalliagh
OL,13,FRoad at around 6pm on Sunday.
OL,15,FOfficers dispersed the crowd and
OL,16,Fmonitored the situation, describing it
OL,17,Fas "calm" by 7pm.
