OL,3,CBoy aged 9 among three children
OL,4,Cdetained following disorder
OL,6,FThree boys aged 9, 12 and 13 were
OL,7,Fdetained, cautioned and taken home to
OL,8,Ftheir parents and are to be referred
OL,9,Fto a youth diversion officer.
OL,11,FChief Inspector Cherith Craig said:
OL,12,F"It is really disappointing to see
OL,13,Fyoung people involved in this type of
OL,14,Fbehaviour.
OL,16,F"We know it is not reflective of the
OL,17,Fcommunity of Galliagh and that this
OL,18,Ftype of reckless activity is not
OL,19,Fsupported by the community.
